---
title: "Enrollment + Runtime Inference — Streaming on Edge"
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant D as Edge device<br/>(Pi 4B / Galaxy)
    participant S as Student model<br/>(INT8 ONNX)
    participant M as Memory<br/>(template, τ_k, τ_s)

    rect rgb(240, 253, 244)
    Note over U,M: Enrollment (one-time, offline, ~60s)
    U->>D: 5 clean utterances of trigger
    loop 5 times
        D->>S: PCEN → trunk → SV branch
        S-->>D: 192-d embedding
    end
    D->>D: mean-pool → L2-normalize
    D->>D: calibrate τ_k, τ_s on user's own<br/>negative speech (2 min)
    D->>M: store template (768 B) + thresholds
    end

    rect rgb(254, 249, 195)
    Note over U,M: Runtime (streaming, 160 ms chunks)
    loop every 160 ms chunk
        U->>D: audio chunk (1600 samples)
        D->>D: PCEN state update (stateful op)
        D->>S: forward (INT8)
        S-->>D: kws_prob, sv_emb
        D->>M: fetch template
        D->>D: cos_sim(sv_emb, template)
        alt kws_prob > τ_k AND cos_sim > τ_s
            D-->>U: ✓ trigger fires
        else
            D-->>U: (silent)
        end
    end
    end
